{
  "stem": "3952.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was one-- there wasn't a well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was one tube coming out from the Earth that was flowing water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was the only water in the camp until we built-- they made a little bit more sophisticated water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You couldn't shower.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were there-- it was very, very miserable at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were fenced in by the British with watchtowers just like the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Except that they wouldn't throw stones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They wouldn't kill you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they were just as bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were bad enough-- bad enough, I would say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Inside the camp, we had our freedom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We would play soccer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We would play ping pong a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We would-- we had a school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My brother-in-law was the director of the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I taught-- I gave a Hebrew lecture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Every morning I had a class.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was the youngest in my class.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was the teacher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And in the afternoon, I gave-- I-- I taught English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "All the teachers of the school, I gave them an English lesson every day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Relatively, a few weeks later when we had already our own showers-- you know, a shower you would set up a pipe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On top of it, you would make a barrel, drill a few holes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It has a thing that you can close the water-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A tab that you can close or open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the shower.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a shower.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was already good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other than that, we had quite a good time, relatively a good time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- they taught us how to-- how to dismantle weapons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, pre-military training, because they needed us, if we go to Israel, that we be ready to be soldiers.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
